#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_read_group
msgid ""
"\n"
"            **Tool Name: Read group**\n"
"\n"
"            Searches a particular model using a domain. The provided domain "
"must be in valid JSON format.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            **工具名称：读取分组**\n"
"\n"
"            使用域搜索特定模型。提供的域必须是有效的 JSON 格式。\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_search
msgid ""
"\n"
"            **Tool Name: search**\n"
"\n"
"            Searches a particular model using a domain. The provided domain "
"must be in valid JSON format.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            **工具名称：搜索**\n"
"\n"
"            使用域搜索特定模型。提供的域必须是有效的 JSON 格式。\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_get_fields
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Lists ONLY searchable fields for a single model that can be used "
"in domain filters and grouping.\n"
"            Essential for building valid domains - if a field isn't listed "
"here, it CANNOT be used.\n"
"\n"
"            Returns format:\n"
"            ```\n"
"            field_name|display_name|type|sortable|groupable|description\n"
"            partner_id|Customer|many2one(res.partner)|true|true|Customer for "
"this order\n"
"            date_order|Order Date|datetime|true|true|Date when order was "
"placed\n"
"            order_line|Order Lines|one2many(sale.order.line)|false|false|"
"Lines in this order\n"
"            state|Status|selection|true|true|Order status\n"
"            ```\n"
"\n"
"            Key points:\n"
"            - ⚠️ Only returns SEARCHABLE fields - others cannot be used in "
"domains\n"
"            - For relationships: Shows related model in parentheses "
"(many2one, one2many, many2many)\n"
"            - Only relationship fields can be used to traverse to other "
"models\n"
"            - Literal fields such as char/text/float CANNOT be used for "
"traversal\n"
"            - 'sortable' indicates if field can be used in order_by "
"parameter\n"
"            - 'groupable' indicates if field can be used for grouping when "
"not available in search view\n"
"\n"
"            💡 Performance tip: When exploring multiple models, call this "
"tool multiple times in ONE message\n"
"            Example: Exploring sale.order, product.product, and res.partner? "
"Make 3 parallel calls.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            仅列出单个模型中可用于域筛选和分组的可搜索字段。\n"
"            对于构建有效域至关重要——如果字段未在此列出，则无法使用。\n"
"\n"
"            返回格式：\n"
"            ```\n"
"            字段名|显示名称|类型|可排序|可分组|描述\n"
"            partner_id|客户|many2one(res.partner)|true|true|此订单的客户\n"
"            date_order|订单日期|datetime|true|true|订单下达日期\n"
"            order_line|订单行|one2many(sale.order.line)|false|false|此订单中"
"的行\n"
"            state|状态|selection|true|true|订单状态\n"
"            ```\n"
"\n"
"            关键点：\n"
"            - ⚠️ 仅返回可搜索字段 - 其他字段不能在域中使用\n"
"            - 对于关系字段：显示括号中的关联模型 (many2one, one2many, "
"many2many)\n"
"            - 只有关系字段可用于遍历到其他模型\n"
"            - 字面字段（如字符/文本/浮点数）不能用于遍历\n"
"            - '可排序' 表示字段是否可用于 order_by 参数\n"
"            - '可分组' 表示当搜索视图中不可用时，字段是否可用于分组\n"
"\n"
"            💡 性能提示：探索多个模型时，在一条消息中多次调用此工具\n"
"            示例：探索 sale.order, product.product 和 res.partner？进行 3 次"
"并行调用。\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_compute_report_measures
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Lists numeric fields (measures) available for aggregation in "
"pivot/graph views.\n"
"            MUST be called before using measures in open_menu_pivot() or "
"open_menu_graph().\n"
"\n"
"            Returns CSV with pipe (|) delimiter:\n"
"            ```\n"
"            field_name|display_name|type|aggregator|sortable\n"
"            __count|Count|integer||true\n"
"            amount_total|Total|monetary|sum|true\n"
"            margin|Margin|float|sum|true\n"
"            quantity|Quantity|float|sum|true\n"
"            ```\n"
"\n"
"            Key points:\n"
"            - __count is always available (counts records)\n"
"            - Only numeric fields with aggregators are returned\n"
"            - Use field_name in measures parameter\n"
"            - For rankings in pivot: Add ordering (e.g., \"amount_total "
"desc\")\n"
"            - Call multiple times in parallel if comparing different menus\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            列出数据透视表/图表视图中可用于聚合的数值字段（度量）。\n"
"            在使用 open_menu_pivot() 或 open_menu_graph() 中的度量之前必须调"
"用。\n"
"            返回以竖线 (|) 分隔的 CSV：\n"
"            ```\n"
"            字段名|显示名称|类型|聚合器|可排序\n"
"            __count|计数|integer||true\n"
"            amount_total|总计|monetary|sum|true\n"
"            margin|利润|float|sum|true\n"
"            quantity|数量|float|sum|true\n"
"            ```\n"
"\n"
"            关键点：\n"
"            -__count 始终可用（记录计数）\n"
"            - 仅返回带有聚合器的数值字段\n"
"            - 在 measures 参数中使用 field_name\n"
"            - 对于数据透视表中的排名：添加排序（例如 “amount_total desc”）\n"
"            - 比较不同菜单时并行多次调用\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_open_menu_graph
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Opens a graph/chart view using search view elements.\n"
"            Best for: Trends, comparisons, distributions, visual KPIs.\n"
"\n"
"            Supported chart types:\n"
"            - 'bar': Compare values across categories\n"
"            - 'line': Show trends over time\n"
"            - 'pie': Display proportions of a whole\n"
"\n"
"            Features:\n"
"            - Apply filters from menu's available options\n"
"            - Visualize a single measure\n"
"            - Group by one field for the chart axis\n"
"            - Search within specific fields\n"
"            - Stacking and cumulation options\n"
"            - Order control (ASC/DESC)\n"
"\n"
"            💡 Call compute_report_measures() first to find valid measures\n"
"            ⚠️ Each search string must use format 'field=text'. Array can "
"contain multiple search strings or be empty []\n"
"            ⚠️ Mode must be exactly 'bar', 'line', or 'pie'\n"
"            ⚠️ Order must be exactly 'ASC' or 'DESC'\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            使用搜索视图元素打开图表/图形视图。\n"
"            最佳用于：趋势、比较、分布、可视化 KPI。\n"
"\n"
"            支持的图表类型：\n"
"            - 'bar'：跨类别比较值\n"
"            - 'line'：显示随时间变化的趋势\n"
"            - 'pie'：显示整体比例\n"
"            功能：\n"
"            - 应用菜单可用选项中的筛选器\n"
"            - 可视化单个度量\n"
"            - 按一个字段分组作为图表轴\n"
"            - 在特定字段中搜索\n"
"            - 堆叠和累积选项\n"
"            - 顺序控制（升序/降序）\n"
"\n"
"            💡 首先调用 compute_report_measures() 以找到有效的度量\n"
"            ⚠️ 每个搜索字符串必须使用格式 'field=text'。数组可包含多个搜索字符"
"串或为空 []\n"
"            ⚠️ 模式必须完全是 'bar'、'line' 或 'pie'\n"
"            ⚠️ 顺序必须完全是 'ASC' 或 'DESC'\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_open_menu_kanban
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Opens a kanban (card-based) view using search view elements.\n"
"            Best for: Stage/status visualization, pipeline views, workflow "
"management.\n"
"\n"
"            Key features:\n"
"            - Display records as cards in columns\n"
"            - Apply filters from menu's available options\n"
"            - Group by workflow stages or other fields\n"
"            - Search within specific fields\n"
"            - Ideal for CRM pipelines, task boards, project workflows\n"
"\n"
"            ⚠️ Use only filter names and groupby fields from menu data\n"
"            ⚠️ Each search string must use format 'field=text'. Array can "
"contain multiple search strings or be empty []\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            使用搜索视图元素打开看板（基于卡片）视图。\n"
"            最佳用于：阶段/状态可视化、管道视图、工作流管理。\n"
"\n"
"            关键功能：\n"
"            - 将记录显示为列中的卡片\n"
"            - 应用菜单可用选项中的筛选器\n"
"            - 按工作流阶段或其他字段分组\n"
"            - 在特定字段中搜索\n"
"            - 适用于 CRM 管道、任务看板、项目工作流\n"
"\n"
"            ⚠️ 仅使用菜单数据中的过滤器名称和分组字段\n"
"            ⚠️ 每个搜索字符串必须使用格式 'field=text'。数组可包含多个搜索字符"
"串或为空 []\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_open_menu_list
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Opens a list (table) view using search view elements.\n"
"            Best for: \"Show me\", \"List all\", detailed record viewing, "
"sorting data.\n"
"\n"
"            Key features:\n"
"            - Apply multiple filters by name (from menu's search view)\n"
"            - Group records by available fields\n"
"            - Search within specific fields for text\n"
"            - Displays records in sortable table format\n"
"            - Ideal for reviewing, filtering, and exporting data\n"
"\n"
"            💡 Use search parameter to filter by any searchable field BEFORE "
"considering custom domains\n"
"            ⚠️ Use only filter names and groupby fields from menu data\n"
"            ⚠️ Each search string must use format 'field=text'. Array can "
"contain multiple search strings or be empty []\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            使用搜索视图元素打开列表（表格）视图。\n"
"            最佳用于：“显示”、“列出所有”、详细记录查看、数据排序。\n"
"\n"
"            关键功能：\n"
"            - 按名称应用多个筛选器（来自菜单的搜索视图）\n"
"            - 按可用字段分组记录\n"
"            - 在特定字段中搜索文本\n"
"            - 以可排序的表格格式显示记录\n"
"            - 适用于审查、筛选和导出数据\n"
"\n"
"            💡 在考虑自定义域之前，使用搜索参数按任何可搜索字段进行筛选\n"
"            ⚠️ 仅使用菜单数据中的筛选器名称和分组字段\n"
"            ⚠️ 每个搜索字符串必须使用格式 'field=text'。数组可包含多个搜索字符"
"串或为空 []\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_open_menu_pivot
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Opens a pivot table with advanced search and filtering.\n"
"            Best for: \"Top N\" queries, rankings, cross-tabulation, "
"performance metrics.\n"
"\n"
"            Key features:\n"
"            - Supports filters from search view\n"
"            - Groups data by rows AND columns simultaneously\n"
"            - Aggregates measures (sum, avg, count)\n"
"            - Supports text search across searchable fields\n"
"            - Excel-like pivot table functionality\n"
"\n"
"            💡 ALWAYS call compute_report_measures() first to get valid "
"measures\n"
"            💡 For rankings: Include ordering in measures (e.g., "
"[\"amount_total desc\"])\n"
"            💡 Use search parameter to filter by any searchable field BEFORE "
"considering custom domains\n"
"            ⚠️ Prefer \"Reporting\" app menus for best pivot experience\n"
"            ⚠️ Each search string must use format 'field=text'. Array can "
"contain multiple search strings or be empty []\n"
"            ⚠️ Note: Uses row_groupbys/col_groupbys (arrays) instead of "
"selected_groupbys\n"
"\n"
"            Example: For \"top salespeople selling office products\":\n"
"            - Use search=[\"categ_id\", \"office\"] if categ_id is "
"searchable\n"
"            - Only use custom_domain if no searchable field matches your "
"needs\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            使用高级搜索和过滤打开数据透视表。\n"
"            最佳用于：\"前 N 名\"查询、排名、交叉制表、绩效指标。\n"
"\n"
"            关键功能：\n"
"            - 支持搜索视图中的筛选器\n"
"            - 同时按行和列分组数据\n"
"            - 聚合度量（求和、平均、计数）\n"
"            - 支持跨可搜索字段的文本搜索\n"
"            - 类似 Excel 的数据透视表功能\n"
"\n"
"            💡 始终首先调用 compute_report_measures() 以获取有效的度量\n"
"            💡 对于排名：在度量中包含排序（例如 [\"amount_total desc\"]）\n"
"            💡 在考虑自定义域之前，使用搜索参数按任何可搜索字段进行筛选\n"
"            ⚠️ 优先使用“报告”应用菜单以获得最佳数据透视表体验\n"
"            ⚠️ 每个搜索字符串必须使用格式 'field=text'。数组可包含多个搜索字符"
"串或为空 []\n"
"            ⚠️ 注意：使用 row_groupbys/col_groupbys（数组）而不是 "
"selected_groupbys\n"
"\n"
"            示例：对于“销售办公产品的顶级销售员”：\n"
"            - 如果 categ_id 可搜索，使用 search=[\"categ_id\", \"office\"]\n"
"            - 只有在没有可搜索字段满足需求时才使用 custom_domain\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_get_menu_details
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Retrieves detailed information (context, domain, search_view) "
"for specific menus.\n"
"            MUST be called before using any open_menu_* tool to get menu-"
"specific details.\n"
"\n"
"            Returns CSV with pipe (|) delimiter:\n"
"            ```\n"
"            menu_id|model_name|context|domain|search_view\n"
"            389|sale.order|{\"search_default_my_quotation\": 1}|[]|"
"<search><fields>...</fields></search>\n"
"            172|account.move|{\"search_default_draft\": 1}|[[\"type\", "
"\"=\", \"out_invoice\"]]|<search>...</search>\n"
"            ```\n"
"\n"
"            Key information:\n"
"            - Context: Default filters/groupings applied when menu opens\n"
"            - Domain: Permanent filters that cannot be removed by users\n"
"            - Search_view: Full XML structure with available filters, "
"groupbys, and searchable fields\n"
"\n"
"            💡 Performance tip: Request multiple menu details in one call "
"when comparing options\n"
"            ⚠️ Always validate the returned model matches your expectations\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            检索特定菜单的详细信息（上下文、域、搜索视图）。\n"
"            在使用任何 open_menu_* 工具之前必须调用以获取菜单特定详情。\n"
"\n"
"            返回以竖线 (|) 分隔的 CSV：\n"
"            ```\n"
"            menu_id|model_name|context|domain|search_view\n"
"            389|sale.order|{\"search_default_my_quotation\": 1}|[]|"
"<search><fields>...</fields></search>\n"
"            172|account.move|{\"search_default_draft\": 1}|[[\"type\", "
"\"=\", \"out_invoice\"]]|<search>...</search>\n"
"            ```\n"
"\n"
"            关键信息：\n"
"            - 上下文：菜单打开时应用的默认筛选器/分组\n"
"            - 域：用户无法移除的永久筛选器\n"
"            - 搜索视图：包含可用筛选器、分组和可搜索字段的完整 XML 结构\n"
"\n"
"            💡 性能提示：比较选项时，在一次调用中请求多个菜单详情\n"
"            ⚠️ 始终验证返回的模型是否符合您的预期\n"
"        "

#. module: ai
#: model:ir.actions.server,ai_tool_description:ai.ir_actions_server_adjust_search
msgid ""
"\n"
"            The user can continue on asking questions and if you think that "
"the current search can just be adjusted without opening a different menu, "
"you can use this tool.\n"
"\n"
"            Provided in the prompt's <session_info_context> is a current "
"view info which contains the active search facets.\n"
"            A facet can be a group of `OR`ed filters, a group of groupbys, "
"or a group of `OR`ed search terms.\n"
"\n"
"            **Understanding the parameters**:\n"
"            - `remove_facets` - Removing a facet removes the whole group of "
"filters/groupbys/search terms. Removing a filter or a search facet reduces "
"the constraints.\n"
"            - `toggle_filters` - Toggling a filter will add/remove a filter "
"from an active filter facet.\n"
"            - `toggle_groupbys` - Toggling a groupby will add/remove a "
"groupby from the active groupbys facet.\n"
"            - `apply_searches` - Applying a search will `OR` the search term "
"on an active search facet containing the same field. E.g., if there is a "
"field facet of \"name=John\" and you provide search \"name=Jane\", the "
"resulting search will be \"name=John OR name=Jane\".\n"
"            - `measures` - Specifying measures will activate the selected "
"measures in the current view if it's a pivot or a graph view.\n"
"            - `mode` - Graph view only: This is the chart type. Choose from "
"\"line\", \"bar\", or \"pie\" to change the chart type in the current graph "
"view.\n"
"            - `order` - Graph view only: Specifying the order will change "
"the sorting of the results in the current graph view.\n"
"            - `stacked` - Graph view only: Specifying stacked will change "
"the stacking of the results in the current graph view.\n"
"            - `cumulated` - Graph view only: Specifying cumulated will "
"change the accumulation of the results in the current graph view.\n"
"            - `custom_domain` - The search view elements may not be "
"sufficient to express the needed domain. In that case, you can provide a "
"custom domain as a JSON string.\n"
"            - `switch_view_type` - Switching the view type will change the "
"current view to the specified type. Select from the available view types in "
"the current view info.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            如果认为当前搜索只需调整而无需打开不同菜单，用户可继续提问并使用"
"此工具。\n"
"\n"
"            提示的 <session_info_context> 中提供了包含当前活动搜索面的当前视"
"图信息。\n"
"           一个面可以是一组 OR 连接的过滤器、一组分组或一组 OR 连接的搜索"
"词。\n"
"\n"
"            **理解参数**:\n"
"            - `remove_facets` - 移除一个面会移除整个过滤器/分组/搜索词组。移"
"除过滤器或搜索面会减少约束。\n"
"            - `toggle_filters` - 切换筛选器将在活动筛选器面中添加/移除一个筛"
"选器。\n"
"            - `toggle_groupbys` - 切换分组将在活动分组面中添加/移除一个分"
"组。\n"
"            - `apply_searches` - 应用搜索将在包含相同字段的活动搜索面上 OR 该"
"搜索词。例如，如果存在 \"name=John\" 的字段面，并且您提供搜索 \"name=Jane\"，"
"则结果搜索将为 \"name=John OR name=Jane\"。\n"
"            - `measures` - 指定度量将在当前视图（如果是数据透视表或图表视图）"
"中激活所选度量。\n"
"            - `mode` - 仅图表视图：这是图表类型。从 \"line\"、\"bar\" 或 "
"\"pie\" 中选择以更改当前图表视图的图表类型。\n"
"            - `order` - 仅图表视图：指定顺序将更改当前图表视图中结果的排"
"序。\n"
"            - `stacked` - 仅图表视图：指定堆叠将更改当前图表视图中结果的堆叠"
"方式。\n"
"            - `cumulated` - 仅图表视图：指定累积将更改当前图表视图中结果的累"
"积方式。\n"
"            - `custom_domain` - 搜索视图元素可能不足以表达所需的域。在这种情"
